title: NEEGO Canon Wireless Photo Printer All-in-one Color Inkjet Printer Print, Copy, Scan and Mobile Device and Tablet Printing with 6 ft Printer Cable
features: POWERFUL PRINTING OPTIONS - With built-in Wi-Fi, this printer makes it easy to print from anywhere in your office. The free app extends printer access to any employee connected to the cloud, ideal for printing from smart phones and tablets. Additionally, PictBridge technology lets you print cord-free from digital cameras. You can also connect the printer to your office network via USB so any connected computer can print.

PRINT COPY AND SCAN - Make presentations stand out with full color, photo quality prints. You can even create larger pictures by combining multiple prints, thanks to the borderless printing option. Automatic duplex printing lets you save paper and folder space, which is ideal for preparing proposals or for archiving company documents.

SAVE DESKTOP SPACE - Replace your office's printer, copier and scanner with the all-in-one design of this PIXMA printer. A compact design saves even more space, while wireless and network printing minimizes the number of cords you need to connect. Fast printing lets multiple employees, or an entire office, share a single printer for cost savings and efficiency. In addition to saving space, the printer also comes with a quiet mode to help reduce background noise in your office.

SIMPLE WIFI SETUP CONNECTION - In just a few clicks, the printer will easily connect to your wireless access point. The built-in wireless features allow for easy printing from almost anywhere in your home.
MULTI PLATFORM COMPATIBILITY - Connect to your network and devices via hi-speed USB, network cable, PictBridge or wireless LAN. Easily print from your compatible Android device. Works with Alexa
